581
00:32:06,660 --> 00:32:07,660
From this day on,

582
00:32:09,020 --> 00:32:10,130
Panyi

583
00:32:10,370 --> 00:32:12,050
is part of Wei.

584
00:32:12,780 --> 00:32:14,290
All of us

585
00:32:14,290 --> 00:32:15,850
are Lord Wei's people.

586
00:32:15,850 --> 00:32:17,940
Yes, like one family! Well said!

587
00:32:17,940 --> 00:32:19,980
The canal is for your benefit.

588
00:32:20,530 --> 00:32:23,330
We ask for your full support,
people of Panyi.

589
00:32:23,330 --> 00:32:25,780
Good! Well said!

590
00:32:29,290 --> 00:32:31,370
Did you tell her about my canal project?

591
00:32:32,180 --> 00:32:34,260
I wouldn't dare act without orders

592
00:32:34,500 --> 00:32:36,420
and ruin your plans.

593
00:32:38,090 --> 00:32:39,660
Then how did she know?

594
00:32:39,810 --> 00:32:41,050
Lord Wei's actions

595
00:32:41,660 --> 00:32:43,700
show he values you much.

596
00:32:44,130 --> 00:32:45,460
To have such a lord

597
00:32:45,460 --> 00:32:46,850
is Panyi's fortune.

598
00:32:47,610 --> 00:32:49,180
May we stand united

599
00:32:49,180 --> 00:32:50,610
with Lord Wei

600
00:32:50,610 --> 00:32:51,810
to fulfill the vision!

601
00:32:52,020 --> 00:32:57,890
Stand united, fulfill the vision!

602
00:32:57,900 --> 00:33:00,330
- Stand united, fulfill the vision!
- Wei Shao crippled Liu Yan,

603
00:33:00,740 --> 00:33:02,130
yet she handed over Panyi

604
00:33:02,130 --> 00:33:04,130
without demands. I...

605
00:33:04,140 --> 00:33:08,970
Stand united, fulfill the vision!

606
00:33:09,050 --> 00:33:20,470
Stand united, fulfill the vision!

607
00:33:20,580 --> 00:33:23,420
Stand united, fulfill the vision!

608
00:33:33,740 --> 00:33:34,660
Tell me,

609
00:33:35,570 --> 00:33:36,610
what do you think of me?

610
00:33:38,850 --> 00:33:40,330
The world says

611
00:33:40,330 --> 00:33:41,850
Lord Wei only conquers cities,

612
00:33:42,130 --> 00:33:44,290
but in Xindu, I studied

613
00:33:44,290 --> 00:33:46,660
the Panyi Annals you gave me.

614
00:33:47,570 --> 00:33:49,660
I noticed the words Yongning Canal

615
00:33:49,660 --> 00:33:51,050
were traced over repeatedly.

616
00:33:51,570 --> 00:33:53,890
Later, reviewing the map of Wei,

617
00:33:54,290 --> 00:33:55,890
I realized

618
00:33:55,890 --> 00:33:57,460
your greatest effort these years

619
00:33:57,460 --> 00:33:59,050
was for building canals.

620
00:33:59,330 --> 00:34:00,940
Truly admirable.

621
00:34:02,810 --> 00:34:05,180
I'll persuade my uncle

622
00:34:05,740 --> 00:34:07,330
to mobilize Yanzhou's strength

623
00:34:07,330 --> 00:34:08,610
in supporting you.

624
00:34:09,220 --> 00:34:10,890
Are you using the canals

625
00:34:11,930 --> 00:34:12,970
as bargaining leverage?

626
00:34:13,450 --> 00:34:14,580
How could I?

627
00:34:15,890 --> 00:34:16,890
This marriage pact

628
00:34:17,660 --> 00:34:19,740
isn't Wei's promise to Yanzhou.

629
00:34:20,540 --> 00:34:22,370
It's your vow to the people

630
00:34:22,370 --> 00:34:24,330
of Wei and Yanzhou.

631
00:34:29,490 --> 00:34:30,660
Do you know why

632
00:34:30,660 --> 00:34:31,890
Bianzhou attacked Xindu

633
00:34:31,890 --> 00:34:34,010
fourteen years ago?

634
00:34:36,580 --> 00:34:38,450
Because my grandfather helped Wei

635
00:34:38,450 --> 00:34:39,780
build the Yongning Canal.

636
00:34:41,260 --> 00:34:44,140
(Qiao)
This map is confidential.

637
00:34:44,450 --> 00:34:46,580
I made a copy for you.

638
00:34:47,180 --> 00:34:49,270
(Liangya, Panyi, Wei State)
Don't let others see it.

639
00:34:50,580 --> 00:34:52,140
Once the Yongning Canal is complete,

640
00:34:52,410 --> 00:34:53,780
Yanzhou and Wei

641
00:34:53,970 --> 00:34:56,290
will be bound like sworn allies.

642
00:34:56,890 --> 00:34:58,370
Bianzhou won't sit idle.

643
00:34:58,810 --> 00:35:00,740
They'll try to

644
00:35:00,740 --> 00:35:02,060
sever this lifeline.

645
00:35:02,330 --> 00:35:03,450
And Panyi

646
00:35:03,580 --> 00:35:05,970
is the vital pass along this lifeline.

647
00:35:07,140 --> 00:35:08,100
It's like...

648
00:35:09,370 --> 00:35:10,330
a heart.

649
00:35:12,060 --> 00:35:14,700
That day I handed you my seal,

650
00:35:15,290 --> 00:35:16,970
it wasn't because I didn't understand.

651
00:35:18,580 --> 00:35:20,580
It was out of remorse and sincerity

652
00:35:21,100 --> 00:35:23,450
that I gave you my heart.

653
00:35:28,180 --> 00:35:29,700
Heart? What heart?

654
00:35:31,140 --> 00:35:32,580
The seal's with me now.

655
00:35:32,850 --> 00:35:33,780
The city's been taken.

656
00:35:34,450 --> 00:35:35,780
I won't give Panyi back to you.

657
00:35:36,180 --> 00:35:37,890
That day, you took the seal

658
00:35:38,060 --> 00:35:39,370
and drove me out of Xindu.

659
00:35:39,370 --> 00:35:40,810
You betrayed me alone.

660
00:35:42,520 --> 00:35:44,700
But now I've rallied Panyi's people

661
00:35:44,700 --> 00:35:45,970
to help you dig the canal.

662
00:35:46,540 --> 00:35:48,220
If you go back on your word again,

663
00:35:48,700 --> 00:35:49,660
the ones you'll betray

664
00:35:50,540 --> 00:35:52,970
are the people of Wei and Yanzhou.

665
00:35:53,230 --> 00:35:54,430
The people of both states.

666
00:35:56,330 --> 00:35:57,660
Lord Wei, how can you bear this?

667
00:36:00,660 --> 00:36:02,260
I can't out-argue you,

668
00:36:04,260 --> 00:36:05,330
but didn't you say

669
00:36:06,410 --> 00:36:07,580
you wouldn't marry?

670
00:36:10,970 --> 00:36:12,370
Lord Wei, you're magnanimous.

671
00:36:12,930 --> 00:36:14,450
My humble heart yearns for you.

672
00:36:18,060 --> 00:36:19,930
What is there to fret about?

673
00:36:20,370 --> 00:36:21,930
None of the Qiaos are capable fighters.

674
00:36:22,330 --> 00:36:23,540
Qiao Gui is critically ill,

675
00:36:23,660 --> 00:36:25,180
and Qiao Ci isn't grown yet.

676
00:36:25,350 --> 00:36:26,190
That leaves two,

677
00:36:26,530 --> 00:36:28,260
one's a coward, and the other is worthless.

678
00:36:28,540 --> 00:36:30,290
Even with ample supplies,

679
00:36:30,580 --> 00:36:32,140
they've got troops but no commanders.

680
00:36:32,970 --> 00:36:34,890
They'd surrender Panyi,

681
00:36:34,890 --> 00:36:36,370
such a crucial stronghold.

682
00:36:36,370 --> 00:36:37,970
Clearly, they're terrified.

683
00:36:38,620 --> 00:36:40,290
Are they?

684
00:36:40,850 --> 00:36:42,540
They just fear our lord might

685
00:36:42,540 --> 00:36:43,450
banish Lady Qiao again.

686
00:36:43,450 --> 00:36:44,660
Would that sound honorable?

687
00:36:45,450 --> 00:36:46,410
Since when has our lord

688
00:36:46,410 --> 00:36:47,370
cared about honor?

689
00:36:50,260 --> 00:36:51,100
Then banish her.

690
00:36:51,330 --> 00:36:52,620
Expel her from Panyi

691
00:36:52,620 --> 00:36:53,970
like what we did in Xindu

692
00:36:53,970 --> 00:36:54,810
last time.

693
00:36:55,340 --> 00:36:56,770
But who knows if some Wang Yan

694
00:36:56,780 --> 00:36:59,010
or Zhang Yan will be waiting outside Panyi

695
00:36:59,180 --> 00:37:00,220
to plunder her dowry?

696
00:37:07,930 --> 00:37:09,010
Mr. Gongsun,

697
00:37:10,260 --> 00:37:11,100
say something?

698
00:37:11,950 --> 00:37:14,270
I dare not bring shame upon you.

699
00:37:15,030 --> 00:37:15,870
Please

700
00:37:16,140 --> 00:37:17,850
make your own decision.

701
00:37:23,970 --> 00:37:25,200
Who knows when we'll meet again

702
00:37:25,200 --> 00:37:26,700
after you leave this time.

703
00:37:27,490 --> 00:37:29,220
Find a place to settle down quickly,

704
00:37:29,220 --> 00:37:30,780
so we can still exchange letters.

705
00:37:32,540 --> 00:37:33,970
Once I find a place to call home,

706
00:37:33,970 --> 00:37:35,180
I'll surely let you know.

707
00:37:36,140 --> 00:37:36,980
Good.

708
00:37:39,140 --> 00:37:41,140
You've never suffered like this before.

709
00:37:41,490 --> 00:37:42,370
If you

710
00:37:43,100 --> 00:37:45,700
must blame someone,

711
00:37:46,060 --> 00:37:48,490
blame our family's lack of warriors.

712
00:37:50,740 --> 00:37:51,580
Whoa.

713
00:37:57,660 --> 00:37:58,850
Fan, My Lady,

714
00:37:58,850 --> 00:38:00,140
a boulder blocks the path ahead.

715
00:38:00,350 --> 00:38:01,190
Rest a while,

716
00:38:01,430 --> 00:38:02,270
I'll move it aside.

717
00:38:04,330 --> 00:38:05,170
Let's go.

718
00:38:26,060 --> 00:38:27,290
We heard

719
00:38:27,290 --> 00:38:29,180
you were exiled from Xindu by Lord Wei,

720
00:38:29,410 --> 00:38:30,810
so we came after you.

721
00:38:31,180 --> 00:38:32,140
On the way,

722
00:38:32,450 --> 00:38:33,970
we encountered Lord Wei's troops

723
00:38:34,110 --> 00:38:35,310
and fought them.

724
00:38:36,650 --> 00:38:37,580
Later, in Panyi,

725
00:38:38,330 --> 00:38:40,140
I clashed with Liu Yan's forces too.

726
00:38:41,260 --> 00:38:42,850
A three-way battle.

727
00:38:43,190 --> 00:38:44,960
You moved through them

728
00:38:44,970 --> 00:38:46,330
like they weren't even there.

729
00:38:52,180 --> 00:38:54,090
He does possess some brute strength.

730
00:38:56,410 --> 00:38:57,620
We're tired from the journey.

731
00:38:57,620 --> 00:38:59,810
Bi Zhi, please go find us some food.

732
00:39:00,260 --> 00:39:01,140
That's easy enough.

733
00:39:03,180 --> 00:39:04,020
Fan,

734
00:39:04,330 --> 00:39:06,060
I have something important to tell you.

735
00:39:06,370 --> 00:39:08,410
This concerns Yanzhou's survival.

736
00:39:08,410 --> 00:39:10,140
You must do your utmost.

737
00:39:11,810 --> 00:39:13,780
At the border where Yanzhou,

738
00:39:13,940 --> 00:39:15,140
Wei, and Bianzhou meet,

739
00:39:15,490 --> 00:39:16,450
there's a county

740
00:39:16,450 --> 00:39:17,580
called Boya.

741
00:39:18,060 --> 00:39:19,490
To sue for peace,

742
00:39:19,490 --> 00:39:20,700
Yanzhou gave up its heart.

743
00:39:20,700 --> 00:39:22,660
Now that Panyi is in Wei Shao's hands,

744
00:39:23,100 --> 00:39:24,160
we've lost the advantage.

745
00:39:24,160 --> 00:39:25,850
We must secure a backup plan

746
00:39:25,850 --> 00:39:27,700
and hold this strategic location.

747
00:39:28,410 --> 00:39:30,260
Our repeated retreats happened

748
00:39:30,260 --> 00:39:32,060
because we had troops but no leaders,

749
00:39:32,060 --> 00:39:33,180
no capable fighters.

750
00:39:33,410 --> 00:39:34,660
With Bi Zhi here,

751
00:39:34,930 --> 00:39:36,700
I believe we can hold it.

752
00:39:40,740 --> 00:39:42,290
Manman says we should go to Boya.

753
00:39:42,620 --> 00:39:43,700
Then we go to Boya.

754
00:39:43,970 --> 00:39:45,030
What kind of place is it?

755
00:39:45,540 --> 00:39:46,660
A county.

756
00:39:48,290 --> 00:39:50,740
It's a good land, near mountains, with mines.

757
00:39:51,890 --> 00:39:52,890
It's also bad.

758
00:39:53,580 --> 00:39:54,970
Everyone wants to take it,

759
00:39:55,100 --> 00:39:56,890
but none dare make the first move.

760
00:39:57,620 --> 00:39:59,780
I don't expect glory from you,

761
00:40:00,180 --> 00:40:02,330
just your safety.

762
00:40:03,490 --> 00:40:04,330
Bi Zhi,

763
00:40:04,850 --> 00:40:06,180
let's just be

764
00:40:06,180 --> 00:40:08,540
a happy ordinary couple, alright?

765
00:40:08,970 --> 00:40:09,810
Alright.

766
00:40:10,700 --> 00:40:11,540
Hyah!

767
00:40:24,410 --> 00:40:25,620
You parted with your sister,

768
00:40:26,260 --> 00:40:27,970
yet you seem unshaken.

769
00:40:29,180 --> 00:40:31,330
My lady has fulfilled a wish,

770
00:40:31,660 --> 00:40:32,620
so she's delightful.

771
00:40:32,780 --> 00:40:33,850
What wish?

772
00:40:34,930 --> 00:40:37,490
Our Qiao family finally has a true warrior.

773
00:40:37,490 --> 00:40:38,370
That Bi Zhi

774
00:40:38,370 --> 00:40:39,580
was born with godlike strength.

775
00:40:41,810 --> 00:40:43,260
What a fine match!

776
00:40:43,410 --> 00:40:45,490
But what of my lady's marriage?

777
00:40:47,100 --> 00:40:48,370
A full day has passed.

778
00:40:48,490 --> 00:40:50,370
Why no word from Lord Wei?

779
00:40:50,580 --> 00:40:51,970
It takes time.

780
00:40:51,970 --> 00:40:53,100
Haste makes waste.

781
00:40:55,660 --> 00:40:56,500
My Lady.

782
00:41:00,730 --> 00:41:01,580
My Lady.

783
00:41:01,600 --> 00:41:03,220
You're missing for a whole day.

784
00:41:03,660 --> 00:41:04,820
Turns out you're here for tea?

785
00:41:07,290 --> 00:41:09,220
You already gave away a city.

786
00:41:09,220 --> 00:41:11,100
Now you promise to build canals?

787
00:41:11,620 --> 00:41:12,700
Patience.

788
00:41:12,850 --> 00:41:13,700
Sit.

789
00:41:13,700 --> 00:41:14,620
I...

790
00:41:18,810 --> 00:41:20,810
We seek an alliance with Wei.

791
00:41:20,810 --> 00:41:22,580
Shouldn't we show sincerity?

792
00:41:23,660 --> 00:41:25,620
And let them keep nibbling at us?

793
00:41:26,540 --> 00:41:29,140
These canals will solve Wei's drought.

794
00:41:29,140 --> 00:41:31,180
Won't that make Lord Wei unstoppable?

795
00:41:31,180 --> 00:41:32,490
You're right.

796
00:41:33,490 --> 00:41:34,970
If this succeeds,

797
00:41:35,220 --> 00:41:37,100
Wei will grow even stronger.

798
00:41:37,330 --> 00:41:39,370
The greater the threat Yanzhou faces.

799
00:41:39,970 --> 00:41:42,370
But these are long-term pros and cons.

800
00:41:43,220 --> 00:41:44,620
For now,

801
00:41:44,970 --> 00:41:46,330
if this succeeds,

802
00:41:46,700 --> 00:41:48,490
the benefits outweigh the risks.

803
00:41:50,700 --> 00:41:52,690
And where do these benefits come from?

804
00:41:53,410 --> 00:41:55,260
Wei Shao's canal project is inevitable.

805
00:41:55,260 --> 00:41:56,100
Even if I refuse,

806
00:41:56,100 --> 00:41:57,450
he'll conduct it anyway.

807
00:41:57,660 --> 00:41:59,740
Secondly, while building the canal,

808
00:41:59,970 --> 00:42:01,740
he'll deploy considerable troops,

809
00:42:01,850 --> 00:42:04,700
leaving no resources to attack Yanzhou.

810
00:42:05,290 --> 00:42:06,620
This gives us

811
00:42:06,890 --> 00:42:09,180
a breathing space.

812
00:42:09,890 --> 00:42:12,180
I'll use this marriage

813
00:42:12,180 --> 00:42:13,450
to turn the tide.

814
00:42:15,180 --> 00:42:16,700
But now it seems

815
00:42:16,700 --> 00:42:17,780
this marriage

816
00:42:18,260 --> 00:42:19,810
