817
00:42:20,620 --> 00:42:21,890
What do you mean?

818
00:42:24,490 --> 00:42:25,370
Lord Qiao Gui...

819
00:42:26,450 --> 00:42:27,290
has passed away.

820
00:42:29,700 --> 00:42:32,010
I came specifically to deliver this news.

821
00:42:36,140 --> 00:42:36,980
Wait,

822
00:42:38,450 --> 00:42:40,930
this is no joking matter.

823
00:43:16,100 --> 00:43:18,980
(Qiao Gui, Governor of Yanzhou,)

824
00:43:24,140 --> 00:43:27,180
(passed peacefully on April 13th, aged 60.)

825
00:43:34,140 --> 00:43:35,620
When did this happen?

826
00:43:36,620 --> 00:43:37,580
Today.

827
00:43:37,780 --> 00:43:38,930
It happens to be

828
00:43:38,930 --> 00:43:40,260
his fifth-week memorial.

829
00:43:40,460 --> 00:43:44,100
(Qiao Gui, Governor of Yanzhou)

830
00:44:04,060 --> 00:44:04,900
My Lady,

831
00:44:05,810 --> 00:44:06,850
building canals

832
00:44:06,970 --> 00:44:08,260
is no small matter.

833
00:44:09,580 --> 00:44:12,290
You can't just act on impulse alone.

834
00:44:27,180 --> 00:44:29,460
(Qiao Gui, Governor of Yanzhou)

835
00:44:40,100 --> 00:44:41,370
My Lady, are you alright?

836
00:44:43,700 --> 00:44:45,700
(passed peacefully on April 13th, aged 60.)

837
00:44:47,010 --> 00:44:49,580
I missed my chance to see him one last time.

