00:45:47,963 --> 00:45:50,793
♪The moonlight is as silent
as the deep sea♪

839
00:45:51,863 --> 00:45:54,323
♪From afar♪

840
00:45:56,273 --> 00:45:59,423
♪It once lit up dreams with a breath♪

841
00:46:00,343 --> 00:46:03,453
♪But vanished with a sigh♪

842
00:46:04,673 --> 00:46:08,043
♪Brushing past my fingertips♪

843
00:46:08,443 --> 00:46:11,813
♪My heartstrings were stirred quietly♪

844
00:46:12,643 --> 00:46:14,583
♪As if we once met before♪

845
00:46:15,073 --> 00:46:19,183
♪Holding back a love so deep♪

846
00:46:21,473 --> 00:46:24,843
♪Love asks for nothing in the end♪

847
00:46:25,433 --> 00:46:28,513
♪Leaving only obsessions♪

848
00:46:29,833 --> 00:46:33,233
♪I've wandered in the world♪

849
00:46:33,733 --> 00:46:36,733
♪Yet cannot have it all♪

850
00:46:38,293 --> 00:46:41,563
♪We meet and part in the fires of war♪

851
00:46:41,883 --> 00:46:45,573
♪Embracing,
leaving tender marks of love♪

852
00:46:46,273 --> 00:46:48,203
♪With one breathtaking glance♪

853
00:46:48,743 --> 00:46:53,663
♪How could I ever forget♪

854
00:46:54,243 --> 00:46:56,523
♪I would cross mountains and seas♪

855
00:46:56,523 --> 00:46:59,043
♪To spend time with you♪

856
00:46:59,293 --> 00:47:00,653
♪When we grow old♪

857
00:47:00,653 --> 00:47:03,243
♪Nothing will change♪

858
00:47:03,243 --> 00:47:04,843
♪The misty rains never cease♪

859
00:47:04,843 --> 00:47:07,703
♪Falling gently on your brow♪

